{"tid":955675,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"三浦翔平桐谷美玲補辦婚宴","createTime":"2018-12-25T15:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T16:37:33.000Z","uid":49197,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bb13895515484ccb8611de76d3e7a65303e39a17","tid":955675,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:04:54.000Z","msg":"祝三浦翔平快d仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20181225/s00008/cee5eb6ea91153e6ca1fa92f01ba30d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20181225%2Fs00008%2Fcee5eb6ea91153e6ca1fa92f01ba30d4.jpg&h=92011bcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三浦翔平（左）和桐谷美玲（右）前晚在東京補辦婚宴，約200名親友到賀。<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】兩年前合演日劇《有喜歡的人》鬧出戲假情真的桐谷美玲和三浦翔平，自去年底爆出戀情後，今年7月正式註冊結婚，並趁女方在本月16日慶祝29歲生辰，先到夏威夷舉行婚禮，前日再於東京某大酒店補辦婚宴，招待200名親友到賀，當中包括《有喜歡的人》拍檔山崎賢人及野村周平、佐藤健、橋本環奈、城田優、波瑠等，相當熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n由於桐谷美玲曾任深夜新聞節目《NEWS ZERO》主持，因此在婚宴開始前播放一段有關新郎新娘的介紹短片，亦刻意採用該節目的風格拍攝，主持人村尾信尚更親臨現場，向一對新人致賀辭。<br />\n<br />\n待婚宴結束後，一對新人公開席上合照，並發表聯名聲明，感謝各界支持和祝福，並承諾二人婚後會互相扶持。"},{"pid":"33cc32fc0c2d3912c5f62d7fe2aa206e652f7ea3","tid":955675,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059d28bdf3332dadf566aa0d601271e70d3cf4cb","tid":955675,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b411eb8e9d7d1a61a3311639aba0b7f56361e9ed","tid":955675,"uid":122139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=